Medicaid API Endpoint Classes

Source: R/S7_caid.R
medicaid.Rd

Medicaid API Endpoint Classes

Usage

caid_endpoint(alias)

caid_group(alias)

caid_temporal(alias)

Arguments

alias

<chr> endpoint alias

Value

An S7 <caid_endpoint>, <caid_group>, or <caid_temporal> object

Examples

caid_endpoint("managed_longterm")
#> <caid_endpoint>
#>  @ identifier: chr "https://data.medicaid.gov/api/1/datastore/query/5394bcab-c748-5e4b-af07-b5bf77ed3aa3/0"
